My VIM configuration files and plugins

To use on linux:
Link .vim/ -> vimfiles/
Link .vimrc -> vimfiles/_vimrc.linux

To use on Windows
Add _vimrc file with "source ~\vimfiles\_vimrc.windows"

To bring in the submodules after cloning,
git submodule init
git submodule update

For Neovim
ln -s ~/.vim ~/.config/nvim
ln -s ~/.vimrc ~/.config/nvim/init.vim
